an entry for the nowJs hackathon: http://nowjs.com/rtt
proj page here: http://crashspace.pbworks.com/w/page/45570359/NowJS%20HackAThon

In theory, NowJS makes realtime we apps easy: http://www.nowjs.org/

How easy? We will see. None of us have used NowJS, node.js, or even written a game. This will primarily be a creative learning effort, but with a timeline... go us.

if you wish to play along start here: https://github.com/Flotype/now


